{"article_id":"jjYHTBdj8RxWv0R8","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Long before Michael Cohen came to Congress","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"to cast President Donald Trump as a `` con man '' and possibly a criminal ,","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"the president 's longtime personal attorney had given doubters plenty","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"to chew on .","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"Cohen arrived at House Oversight and Government Reform Committee 's much-anticipated hearing on Wednesday","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"just two months removed from pleading guilty to lying to Congress about his own dealings with Trump .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"And a little more than two months from now , Cohen must begin a three-year prison sentence","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"that has raised as many questions about his own credibility as that of his former boss ,","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"whom Cohen called a \" racist , \" a \" con man \" and a \" cheat . \"","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"Cohen ,","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"who once boasted","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"that he would take a bullet for the president ,","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"said","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"Trump implicitly encouraged him to lie to Congress in 2017 about the pursuit of a Moscow tower project ;","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"ordered hush money payments to women in violation of campaign finance laws ;","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"and knew in advance","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"that WikiLeaks would release stolen emails from Hillary Clinton .","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"Over six hours of sworn testimony , Cohen linked Trump more directly than ever to the criminal investigations","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"that have loomed over his presidency .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"Start the day smarter :","depth":5},{"id":21,"text":"Get 's Daily Briefing in your inbox","depth":5},{"id":22,"text":"And he offered congressional lawmakers a road map to witnesses and documents","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"he said","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"could corroborate his claims","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"for congressional investigators","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"examining the president and his businesses .","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"Still ,","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"while committee chairman Elijah Cummings , D-Md. , billed the extraordinary hearing as a \" search for the truth , \"","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"the spectacle ended more than six hours later with the same basic question","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"as when it began :","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"Whom to believe ?","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"`` Some will certainly ask ,","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"'If Mr. Cohen was lying then","depth":15},{"id":34,"text":"( when he defended Trump for more than a decade as his trusted attorney ) ,","depth":15},{"id":35,"text":"why should we believe him now ? ''","depth":14},{"id":36,"text":"Cummings asked .","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"`` That is a legitimate question . ''","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"The question","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"posed by the chairman","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"would later track an oft-repeated refrain by Republican committee members","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"whose attacks on Cohen 's veracity shadowed the attorney 's stunning accounts of his boss ' conduct .","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"`` Anything","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"that Michael Cohen asserts","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"comes combined with credibility issues .","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"That 's just par for the course , ''","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"said Renato Mariotti , a former federal prosecutor in Chicago .","depth":10},{"id":47,"text":"`` But , it 's not a high bar","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"to be more truthful than Trump on these issues . ''","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"Indeed , Trump has offered a series of conflicting statements about hush money deals to quiet women","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"who said","depth":12},{"id":51,"text":"they had affairs with him ,","depth":12},{"id":52,"text":"first saying","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"he knew nothing of the payments","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"then admitting","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"they `` came from me . ''","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"It all came to a head Wednesday","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"when Cohen offered Congress copies of checks with Trump 's distinctive signature","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"that","depth":14},{"id":59,"text":"Cohen said","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"were made","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"to repay him for the hush money deals .","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"Lawmakers , Republicans and Democrats alike , agreed","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"Cohen had lied in the past ,","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"but they disagreed","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"whether his word should be trusted now .","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"Cummings , after the hearing , said","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"he found Cohen believable","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"and thought","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"the hearing shed new light","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"on whether the president may have committed a crime .","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"Yet throughout the daylong spectacle , Republicans cast Cohen as a liar","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"- someone","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"who sought to gain financially from book and TV deals","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"by bashing the president .","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"Republican Rep. Paul Gosar put it plainly :","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"`` Look at the old adage","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"that our moms taught us :","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"'Liar , liar , pants on fire . ' No one should ever listen to you","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"and give you credibility .","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"It 's sad . ''","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"Trump 's campaign even chimed in ,","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"calling Cohen a felon , liar","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"and questioning the evidence","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"Cohen provided to Congress .","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"`` Michael Cohen is a felon , a disbarred lawyer , and a convicted perjurer","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"who lied to both Congress and the special counsel in a deliberate and premeditated fashion , ''","depth":10},{"id":87,"text":"campaign spokeswoman Kayleigh McEnany said .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"`` This is the same Michael Cohen","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"who has admitted","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"that he lied to Congress previously .","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"Why did they even bother to swear him in this time ? ''","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"Throughout the hours of testimony , Republicans repeatedly asserted","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"that Cohen had admitted to lying to Congress","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"and was testifying in hopes for a lighter prison sentence .","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"Mariotti said","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"Cohen 's testimony would n't change the three-year sentence","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"handed down by a judge ,","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"adding","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"that his comments were just of accounts","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"that he has already provided to prosecutors .","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"But there were very real risks .","depth":9},{"id":102,"text":"Among those certain to have monitored Cohen 's testimony were federal prosecutors in Manhattan and those","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"assigned to Russia special counsel Robert Mueller .","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"Both teams have obtained testimony from Cohen for their investigations","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"and probably want to be sure Cohen 's testimony","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"before Congress tracks the information","depth":14},{"id":107,"text":"he has provided them .","depth":14},{"id":108,"text":"Any slip could cost him a chance at reduced prison time or new criminal charges","depth":14},{"id":109,"text":"for lying to Congress . `` Of course , Cohen appearing before Congress was n't an act of charity .","depth":14},{"id":110,"text":"He wants to improve his public reputation ,","depth":14},{"id":111,"text":"which has been decimated , ''","depth":14},{"id":112,"text":"Mariotti said .","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"`` And to a large part , I think","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"this has helped . ''","depth":12},{"id":115,"text":"Federal prosecutors already have backed parts of Cohen 's account .","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"Justice Department lawyers said in a court filing in December","depth":11},{"id":117,"text":"that Cohen made hush money payments to two women at Trump 's direction .","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"And Cohen confirmed on Wednesday","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"that he was continuing to cooperate with federal investigators","depth":12},{"id":120,"text":"who seized records from his home and office","depth":13},{"id":121,"text":"and customarily seek out evidence far broader than the word of someone","depth":14},{"id":122,"text":"trying to earn himself a shorter prison sentence .","depth":14},{"id":123,"text":"Elizabeth de la Vega , a federal prosecutor of 20 years , said","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"she found Cohen believable ,","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"adding","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"that conservatives on the committee did n't seem to even dispute the nature of Cohen 's allegations ,","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"attacking only his character .","depth":12},{"id":128,"text":"`` The one glaring thing","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"they did not do","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"was talk about any of the facts , ''","depth":12},{"id":131,"text":"de la Vega said .","depth":11},{"id":132,"text":"`` They just hammered on what we know :","depth":11},{"id":133,"text":"Michael Cohen has lied","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"and done bad things . ''","depth":12},{"id":135,"text":"Helping his case ,","depth":8},{"id":136,"text":"Cohen sought to prove some of his claims with documents","depth":9},{"id":137,"text":"he kept during his decade","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"working under Trump as his right-hand man .","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"He brought along copies of checks , one","depth":11},{"id":140,"text":"signed by Trump","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"while he was president ,","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"that","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"Cohen said","depth":12},{"id":144,"text":"was repayment for a hush money deal with porn star Stormy Daniels","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"after she said","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"she had an affair with the president .","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"Cohen also included a letter","depth":13},{"id":148,"text":"he sent ,","depth":13},{"id":149,"text":"which he claimed","depth":13},{"id":150,"text":"Trump directed him to write ,","depth":13},{"id":151,"text":"in which he threatened the president 's alma mater with a lawsuit","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"if his grades were released .","depth":12},{"id":153,"text":"He also provided copies of documents","depth":13},{"id":154,"text":"detailing Trump 's finances for several years","depth":13},{"id":155,"text":"and said","depth":13},{"id":156,"text":"Trump inflated his assets","depth":14},{"id":157,"text":"to get better insurance rates and loans from banks .","depth":14},{"id":158,"text":"The documents offered support for some of Cohen 's claims","depth":13},{"id":159,"text":"- particularly that Trump had personally reimbursed him for the 2016 payoffs -","depth":13},{"id":160,"text":"but did little to corroborate others .","depth":12},{"id":161,"text":"Cohen 's attorney , Lanny Davis , had released a secretly recorded audio recording of Trump","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"that showed","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"the president was aware and approved of the scheme","depth":11},{"id":164,"text":"to quiet claims by women .","depth":11},{"id":165,"text":"`` You have to look at the big picture , ''","depth":10},{"id":166,"text":"de la Vega pointed out .","depth":10},{"id":167,"text":"She said","depth":12},{"id":168,"text":"the test of truth should n't just focus on Wednesday and Cohen 's testimony .","depth":12},{"id":169,"text":"It 's about the whole of what is known","depth":12},{"id":170,"text":"and the information","depth":13},{"id":171,"text":"still being investigated by federal prosecutors in New York and by Mueller .","depth":13},{"id":172,"text":"`` This test of credibility is about everyone and everything","depth":13},{"id":173,"text":"we know thus far , ''","depth":13},{"id":174,"text":"de la Vega said .","depth":12},{"id":175,"text":"`` You have all these other factors and evidence","depth":12},{"id":176,"text":"that 's been part of a number of cases . ''","depth":12},{"id":177,"text":"Even if lawmakers do not believe Cohen ,","depth":9},{"id":178,"text":"he left them with names of other witnesses and a trail","depth":10},{"id":179,"text":"to follow","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"in investigating Trump 's businesses , his presidential campaign and whether there is any truth to his former lawyer 's searing accusations .","depth":11},{"id":181,"text":"`` The question becomes :","depth":10},{"id":182,"text":"Where do we go from here ? ''","depth":10},{"id":183,"text":"Cummings said after Wednesday 's hearing .","depth":9},{"id":184,"text":"He said","depth":11},{"id":185,"text":"that between Cohen 's testimony and evidence , lawmakers have a lot to study .","depth":11},{"id":186,"text":"`` If you asked me exactly where we 're going ,","depth":13},{"id":187,"text":"I ca n't tell you exactly the areas","depth":14},{"id":188,"text":"we 'll go in ,","depth":14},{"id":189,"text":"but we will do things in a very methodical way , a very careful way , ''","depth":12},{"id":190,"text":"he said .","depth":11},{"id":191,"text":"`` I thought","depth":12},{"id":192,"text":"( Cohen ) brought a lot to the table ;","depth":12},{"id":193,"text":"he described the Donald Trump","depth":12},{"id":194,"text":"that he knows .","depth":12},{"id":195,"text":"And we 'll see","depth":11},{"id":196,"text":"where we go from there . ''","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":393,"left":0,"right":392,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":392,"left":215,"right":391,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":215,"left":200,"right":214,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":200,"left":198,"right":199,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":198,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":199,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":214,"left":204,"right":213,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":201,"right":203,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":201,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":7,"right":202,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":213,"left":211,"right":212,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":211,"left":207,"right":210,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":207,"left":206,"right":13,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":206,"left":10,"right":205,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":205,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":210,"left":14,"right":209,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":209,"left":15,"right":208,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":208,"left":16,"right":17,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":212,"left":18,"right":19,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":391,"left":221,"right":390,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":221,"left":216,"right":220,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":216,"left":20,"right":21,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":220,"left":218,"right":219,"relation